1
00:01:22,220 --> 00:01:29,940
[Legend of Zang Hai]

2
00:01:30,060 --> 00:01:32,900
[Episode 20]

3
00:01:36,660 --> 00:01:46,210
[Prince Yongrong's Mansion]

4
00:01:46,210 --> 00:01:47,930
Should any guest arrive, direct them

5
00:01:47,930 --> 00:01:48,870
to the side entrance.

6
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:49,700
Yes, sir.

7
00:01:58,540 --> 00:01:59,940
[Prince Yongrong's Mansion]

8
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:06,180
I am Zang Hai, the Imperial Astronomer. I have come to call on His Highness.

9
00:02:06,510 --> 00:02:07,690
My visiting card was presented yesterday.

10
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,130
Ah, Mr. Zang.

11
00:02:09,460 --> 00:02:10,210
Please come with me.

12
00:02:19,410 --> 00:02:21,600
His Highness said today that fortune comes from the west,

13
00:02:21,740 --> 00:02:23,440
so only the west gate will be opened.

14
00:02:24,190 --> 00:02:26,210
His Highness is so particular about feng shui as well?

15
00:02:27,150 --> 00:02:27,660
Yes.

16
00:02:29,910 --> 00:02:31,170
Mr. Zang, this way, please.

17
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,410
Please wait here for now.

18
00:02:36,630 --> 00:02:38,060
You will be summoned in due order.

19
00:02:57,150 --> 00:02:57,780
Mr. Zang,

20
00:02:58,180 --> 00:02:59,730
please write down your birth characters.

21
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:00,890
His Highness will review them shortly.

22
00:03:05,580 --> 00:03:08,020
[Zang Hai's birth characters]

23
00:03:13,630 --> 00:03:14,980
This Zang Hai

24
00:03:17,310 --> 00:03:18,340
is rather interesting.

25
00:03:24,650 --> 00:03:25,430
May I have your name, sir?

26
00:03:26,420 --> 00:03:28,340
Zhang Huai. That's "Zhang" with the "li" and "zao" radicals.

27
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,290
May I ask which of you is Mr. Zang?

28
00:03:30,630 --> 00:03:31,410
That would be me.

29
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,820
I am Shen Yong, Assistant Minister of the Court of Imperial Entertainments.

30
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,660
His Highness wishes to speak with you in the front hall.

31
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:37,660
Please come with me.

32
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:12,450
Your Highness.

33
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:18,100
I am Zang Hai, Imperial Astronomer, here to pay my respects to Your Highness.

34
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,020
Zang Hai,

35
00:04:30,630 --> 00:04:31,900
so we meet at last.

36
00:04:33,430 --> 00:04:34,540
The imperial mausoleum incident

37
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:40,290
once led me to believe your fate was clouded by misfortune,

38
00:04:41,190 --> 00:04:44,410
with your Four Pillars governed by yin and your father's life cut short.

39
00:04:44,750 --> 00:04:46,660
But upon seeing your birth characters,

40
00:04:47,430 --> 00:04:48,410
I was surprised to find that you are blessed

41
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:52,220
with the fate of a Heavenly Noble, one who turns adversity into fortune,

42
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,980
with helping hands in hardship

43
00:04:54,550 --> 00:04:55,840
and salvation in danger.

44
00:04:56,630 --> 00:04:57,610
Remarkable.

45
00:04:59,630 --> 00:05:01,900
No wonder you have risen so quickly.

46
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:05,410
I have heard you made bold changes upon taking up your new post.

47
00:05:06,430 --> 00:05:07,540
It seems you are at the height of your powers.

48
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,140
I am deeply humbled, Your Highness.

49
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:12,100
You are of royal blood.

50
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:14,540
How could I, a mere official, presume to be called "noble" by you?

51
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:17,370
Still, you pique my curiosity.

52
00:05:18,690 --> 00:05:20,480
You seem a man born under a cursed fate,

53
00:05:21,310 --> 00:05:22,660
yet your destiny tells a different story.

54
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,500
Let me guess.

55
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:31,050
Has your fate been altered?

56
00:05:32,510 --> 00:05:34,100
I indeed lost both my parents

57
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:36,220
at a young age, left lonely and helpless.

58
00:05:36,430 --> 00:05:38,900
Yet my fate is not governed solely by yin.

59
00:05:39,510 --> 00:05:42,370
At the imperial mausoleum, I was truly set up by others.

60
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,780
He dared to deceive His Majesty over a matter of national mourning.

61
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,780
Chu Huaiming's death

62
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:48,290
was well deserved.

63
00:05:49,190 --> 00:05:50,290
Thank you, Your Highness.

64
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:57,170
This humble gift is but a token of my respect.

65
00:05:57,630 --> 00:05:58,850
May Your Highness kindly accept it.

66
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:22,410
Collecting a full set of Zhenyou Tongbao

67
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:23,980
is uncommon as it stands,

68
00:06:25,070 --> 00:06:26,980
let alone finding one in such excellent condition.

69
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,460
Where did you obtain them?

70
00:06:31,950 --> 00:06:34,140
This set of Zhenyou Tongbao is indeed rare.

71
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,140
I acquired it by chance

72
00:06:36,190 --> 00:06:38,610
from a well-traveled merchant.

73
00:06:39,070 --> 00:06:39,930
I now offer it to Your Highness.

74
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,700
Well-informed, aren't you?

75
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,140
But I like that.

76
00:06:50,430 --> 00:06:50,900
Now tell me.

77
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:52,490
What is it you're after?

78
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,490
I dare not presume too much, Your Highness.

79
00:06:55,270 --> 00:06:58,050
I've heard much of Your Highness's refined taste and noble character,

80
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,730
and have long admired you.

81
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:02,100
I only hoped for the honor of meeting you

82
00:07:02,630 --> 00:07:04,540
and perhaps receiving a few words of your guidance.

83
00:07:07,630 --> 00:07:08,460
Guidance, you say?

84
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,700
You serve the Marquis of Pingjin.

85
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:14,220
Surely you know that's a big taboo in the official circles.

86
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,170
Say something.

87
00:07:22,430 --> 00:07:24,040
Weren't you known for your silver tongue?

88
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:27,980
Why have you suddenly gone mute in front of me?

89
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,850
Your Highness stands second only to His Majesty.

90
00:07:34,310 --> 00:07:35,730
While I waited earlier,

91
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,700
I saw others leave disheartened,

92
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:39,810
and feared that the humble gift I brought

93
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,140
might not catch your eye.

94
00:07:41,950 --> 00:07:44,850
Now that Your Highness finds it pleasing, I consider myself most fortunate.

95
00:07:45,830 --> 00:07:47,610
I dare not harbor any further presumptuous thoughts.

96
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:50,730
I spoke out of turn earlier. Please forgive me, Your Highness.

97
00:07:54,630 --> 00:07:55,600
Forgive!

98
00:07:55,970 --> 00:07:57,290
Forgive!

99
00:07:57,650 --> 00:07:58,450
Forgive!

100
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:03,140
This creature actually knows how to plead.

101
00:08:03,390 --> 00:08:04,490
It's surprisingly clever.

102
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:07,810
Many come to my mansion with presents.

103
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,250
If I accepted them all,

104
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:13,540
my household would be in chaos.

105
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:16,810
Usually, those whose gifts are accepted

106
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,850
are eager to ask for something in return.

107
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:24,610
Yet you seem to be holding back.

108
00:08:25,190 --> 00:08:25,730
What is it?

109
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:30,370
Are you planning to secure something big with a long-term strategy?

110
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:31,730
I wouldn't dare.

111
00:08:33,030 --> 00:08:33,820
Truth be told,

112
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:35,840
ever since I joined the Imperial Astronomical Bureau,

113
00:08:36,270 --> 00:08:37,820
I have come to realize how perilous an official's path truly is.

114
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:41,220
I fear that someday I might share the same tragic end as Chu Huaiming.

115
00:08:41,550 --> 00:08:44,180
I hope to meet wise mentors and trustworthy friends

116
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:45,460
and broaden my horizons.

117
00:08:49,390 --> 00:08:50,980
Why didn't you just say that earlier?

118
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:55,040
Most officials in the Capital

119
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,420
come to me

120
00:08:56,670 --> 00:09:00,420
with the same intentions as you.

121
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,650
Why are you still on your knees?

122
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:05,680
Shen Yong,

123
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,610
help Mr. Zang up.

124
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:08,490
Yes, Your Highness.

125
00:09:10,630 --> 00:09:11,220
Mr. Zang.

126
00:09:17,750 --> 00:09:18,590
Let me ask you this.

127
00:09:19,150 --> 00:09:21,220
You say I have refined taste,

128
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:25,850
but the things I love most reek of money.

129
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,140
Where's the refinement in that?

130
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:30,010
As I made my way here,

131
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:32,420
I couldn't help but notice the elegance in every flower, tree,

132
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:33,850
and blade of grass in Your Highness's courtyard.

133
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:36,490
That gnarled and vigorous desert poplar,

134
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:38,770
twisting like a coiled dragon,

135
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:41,420
has stood for over a thousand years.

136
00:09:42,630 --> 00:09:43,920
I daresay that single tree alone

137
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:46,220
is worth ten years of my humble salary.

138
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,460
You've got quite the discerning eye.

139
00:09:49,150 --> 00:09:53,060
I had that tree brought back alive from the desert.

140
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,980
It took quite the effort.

141
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,650
Yet others come by

142
00:09:57,870 --> 00:10:00,480
and wonder why I've placed

143
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:02,340
a withered, lifeless tree in my courtyard.

144
00:10:03,270 --> 00:10:05,980
Few recognize its worth, as you do.

145
00:10:06,870 --> 00:10:08,610
Having assumed the role of Imperial Astronomer,

146
00:10:09,150 --> 00:10:12,610
I've devoted myself to advancing my expertise in geomancy and object appraisal.

147
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:14,420
I once fancied myself knowledgeable,

148
00:10:15,550 --> 00:10:17,740
but after visiting Your Highness's mansion today,

149
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:20,700
I see how much remains beyond my grasp.

150
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,490
You're certainly well-spoken.

151
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,770
I do like the gift you've brought,

152
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:29,490
but giving gifts in official circles

153
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,420
requires a bit of finesse.

154
00:10:35,790 --> 00:10:37,940
I can show you the proper way.

155
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:40,940
Shen Yong.

156
00:10:41,630 --> 00:10:42,010
Yes, Your Highness.

157
00:10:42,550 --> 00:10:43,870
Today, Mr. Zang

158
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:47,060
is giving you this Zhenyou Tongbao collection.

159
00:10:47,910 --> 00:10:48,340
Yes, Your Highness.

160
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:53,130
Shen Yong,

161
00:10:54,510 --> 00:10:56,770
that's a fine collection you have there.

162
00:10:57,510 --> 00:10:58,100
Your Highness,

163
00:10:58,270 --> 00:10:59,830
this set of Zhenyou Tongbao was gifted

164
00:10:59,830 --> 00:11:01,540
by Mr. Zang of the Imperial Astronomical Bureau.

165
00:11:01,870 --> 00:11:04,060
He says it is an exceedingly rare treasure.

166
00:11:04,870 --> 00:11:06,850
As you know, I lack the expertise to fully appreciate it.

167
00:11:07,630 --> 00:11:10,530
Perhaps you could give me something from your collection

168
00:11:11,030 --> 00:11:13,010
so we can exchange and appreciate each other's treasures.

169
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:15,490
Look at you, so greedy.

170
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:17,610
I won't take it from you for free.

171
00:11:27,670 --> 00:11:28,180
See?

172
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:31,850
Now you're not simply here to present me with treasures.

173
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:34,980
You and Mr. Shen are friends, after all.

174
00:11:37,670 --> 00:11:40,660
It brings me great joy to have received such a precious set today.

175
00:11:41,150 --> 00:11:42,620
I'll surely have a few more drinks tonight.

176
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:45,370
Shen Yong,

177
00:11:46,450 --> 00:11:48,280
since this new friend of yours

178
00:11:48,670 --> 00:11:49,920
is eager to see the world,

179
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:52,700
why not invite him to join the banquet tonight?

180
00:11:54,030 --> 00:11:55,100
Your Highness is absolutely right.

181
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:59,650
Mr. Zang, would you be willing to accompany us?

182
00:12:00,390 --> 00:12:01,630
It would be my utmost pleasure.

183
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:02,700
Thank you, Your Highness.

184
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:08,460
That outfit of yours is somewhat modest.

185
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,300
Shen Yong,

186
00:12:10,910 --> 00:12:13,050
get Mr. Zang something more suitable to wear.

187
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:14,220
Yes, Your Highness.

188
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,820
Congratulations, Mr. Zang.

189
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:26,340
This is no ordinary banquet.

190
00:12:26,870 --> 00:12:27,650
After tonight,

191
00:12:28,030 --> 00:12:29,940
you won't be the same as before.

192
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:42,460
His Highness's night banquets occur once every three years

193
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:45,700
and are never held at the same venue twice.

194
00:12:45,910 --> 00:12:47,060
If it weren't for His Highness's banquet,

195
00:12:47,510 --> 00:12:48,220
who else in the Capital

196
00:12:48,630 --> 00:12:50,610
could book the entire Zhen Tower?

197
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:53,730
You probably don't know many people here today.

198
00:12:53,910 --> 00:12:55,520
Shall I tell you who's here?

199
00:12:56,620 --> 00:12:57,610
Much obliged, Mr. Shen.

200
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:01,850
The gentleman seated to the left of the main seat

201
00:13:01,870 --> 00:13:04,300
is Minister of Rites, Mr. Huang Shen.

202
00:13:04,910 --> 00:13:07,530
Apart from His Highness, he is the highest-ranking official present today.

203
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:09,010
Next to Mr. Huang is Han Lun,

204
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:11,630
Right Administration Vice Commissioner of the Huguang Region.

205
00:13:11,910 --> 00:13:13,180
Being from the same area,

206
00:13:13,550 --> 00:13:15,610
they are likely reminiscing about old times.

207
00:13:16,750 --> 00:13:18,100
The gentleman seated to the right of the main seat

208
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:20,250
is Wang Shiqi, Vice Minister of Personnel.

209
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:22,100
Next to him

210
00:13:22,150 --> 00:13:24,850
is Li Fu, the Left Administration Vice Commissioner of Dingzhou.

211
00:13:25,150 --> 00:13:27,300
What do you suppose they are discussing?

212
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,300
Perhaps Li Fu is asking Mr. Wang

213
00:13:29,630 --> 00:13:31,180
to have him transferred back to the Capital?

214
00:13:33,790 --> 00:13:36,220
As the saying goes, "The sky is high and the Emperor is far away."

215
00:13:36,750 --> 00:13:38,340
With so many influential officials in the Capital,

216
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:41,180
why would a local official, the highest authority

217
00:13:41,480 --> 00:13:42,650
in his own domain,

218
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:45,610
choose to return to the Capital and serve under others?

219
00:13:47,550 --> 00:13:49,610
It is better to be a big fish in a small pond than a small fish in a big pond.

220
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:50,980
Mr. Zang,

221
00:13:51,390 --> 00:13:54,770
talking like that, you sound anything but a newcomer to official circles.

222
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:58,980
No wonder His Highness holds you in such high regard.

223
00:13:59,390 --> 00:14:00,340
You flatter me, Mr. Shen.

224
00:14:03,270 --> 00:14:04,100
Your Highness is here.

225
00:14:04,790 --> 00:14:05,180
Your Highness.

226
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:05,820
His Highness is here.

227
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:10,650
Greetings, Your Highness.

228
00:14:12,510 --> 00:14:13,420
You're all here.

229
00:14:13,760 --> 00:14:14,560
Mr. Wang.

230
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:16,880
The one who arrived with His Highness

231
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:18,760
is Zhang Keshu, Grand Coordinator of Luzhou.

232
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:19,650
Mr. Huang.

233
00:14:20,030 --> 00:14:20,650
Your Highness.

234
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:24,180
Thank you all for waiting.

235
00:14:26,390 --> 00:14:28,530
Allow me to introduce a new face to you:

236
00:14:28,870 --> 00:14:31,370
Zang Hai, Imperial Astronomer,

237
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:33,250
a man of exceptional talent.

238
00:14:35,150 --> 00:14:36,060
I am Zang Hai.

239
00:14:36,510 --> 00:14:37,530
Thanks to His Highness's gracious favor,

240
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:40,340
I have the privilege to meet all of you today.

241
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:42,650
I've read Mr. Zang's memorials.

242
00:14:43,150 --> 00:14:45,650
He certainly has a bold and decisive style.

243
00:14:46,250 --> 00:14:48,180
In that case, you'd better be careful today

244
00:14:48,580 --> 00:14:49,980
and not offend Mr. Zang.

245
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:51,730
I wouldn't dare.

246
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:53,650
In terms of drafting memorials,

247
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:56,460
I must admit I am but a novice compared to all of you.

248
00:14:59,630 --> 00:15:00,300
Zang Hai,

249
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:03,360
we are all officials serving the same court,

250
00:15:04,030 --> 00:15:06,530
and they are quite close to me.

251
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:08,610
You're new to official circles,

252
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:11,880
instead of coming to me all the time,

253
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:15,650
you should be asking them for help more.

254
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:20,060
Many thanks, Your Highness.

255
00:15:20,870 --> 00:15:21,420
All right.

256
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:24,300
There's no need for formalities at my banquet.

257
00:15:24,750 --> 00:15:26,630
Just enjoy yourselves to the fullest.

258
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:27,890
Now, if you please.

259
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:36,250
I'm sure you've all met His Majesty.

260
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:40,010
So let's raise the first cup to him

261
00:15:40,670 --> 00:15:42,340
and wish him good health.

262
00:15:42,670 --> 00:15:44,890
May you all join forces

263
00:15:45,410 --> 00:15:46,850
to support my brother in his duties.

264
00:15:47,390 --> 00:15:47,890
Cheers.

265
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:49,080
- Cheers. - Cheers.

266
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:50,030
- Cheers. - Cheers.

267
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:04,980
Mr. Zang,

268
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:08,130
