273
00:16:19,960 --> 00:16:21,250
and even schemed against others.

274
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:24,010
Had he chosen to serve under me back then,

275
00:16:24,630 --> 00:16:27,820
he might not have been exiled.

276
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:29,180
Then again,

277
00:16:29,870 --> 00:16:31,490
I doubt I would've taken him in.

278
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:32,530
