00:31:01,590 --> 00:31:02,330
No need.

544
00:31:03,390 --> 00:31:04,610
Here is fine.

545
00:31:06,870 --> 00:31:07,500
Your Highness,

546
00:31:08,550 --> 00:31:10,290
your Gui Seal is missing.

547
00:31:12,630 --> 00:31:13,850
The Gui Seal?

548
00:31:15,440 --> 00:31:16,130
Where is it?

549
00:31:16,830 --> 00:31:17,610
Where is it?

550
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:19,900
But Mr. Zang,

551
00:31:20,480 --> 00:31:21,980
His Highness truly likes you,

552
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:24,290
He even granted you some liquor to drink.

553
00:31:25,920 --> 00:31:27,740
This wine is indeed top-grade.

554
00:31:28,550 --> 00:31:31,210
I've never seen His Highness get drunk so quickly before.

555
00:31:32,240 --> 00:31:34,000
So how is His Highness now?

556
00:31:34,790 --> 00:31:35,450
Don't worry.

557
00:31:36,110 --> 00:31:38,540
I just gave him a special hangover cure powder.

558
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:41,220
He'll sober up in no time.

559
00:31:45,790 --> 00:31:47,570
Have you really never seen the Gui Seal?

560
00:32:10,440 --> 00:32:11,260
Stop right there.

561
00:32:13,870 --> 00:32:14,770
Who are you?

562
00:32:19,070 --> 00:32:20,850
I am here to serve Your Highness.

563
00:32:22,040 --> 00:32:25,370
Were you talking to me just now?

564
00:32:50,520 --> 00:32:51,090
Tell me.

565
00:32:52,070 --> 00:32:53,290
What did you just do?

566
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:06,570
Your Highness.

567
00:33:08,040 --> 00:33:08,500
Look

568
00:33:09,680 --> 00:33:10,330
what I found here.

569
00:33:12,070 --> 00:33:14,770
You left the Zhesan coin on the couch outside.

570
00:33:15,310 --> 00:33:16,470
If it gets lost,

571
00:33:16,790 --> 00:33:18,980
where am I supposed to find another one?

572
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:28,180
I really drank too much today.

573
00:33:31,870 --> 00:33:33,050
Why are you still standing there?

574
00:33:33,520 --> 00:33:36,330
Go fetch another spittoon for His Highness.

575
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:38,290
Go now!

576
00:33:41,680 --> 00:33:42,940
Well done, Zang Hai.

577
00:33:44,110 --> 00:33:47,500
You've brought me another one of these Zhesan coins.

578
00:33:49,790 --> 00:33:50,980
Your Highness,

579
00:33:51,550 --> 00:33:52,130
how about

580
00:33:52,680 --> 00:33:56,020
granting me another cup of your fine liquor?

581
00:33:57,630 --> 00:33:59,620
I was mocked when I drank

582
00:33:59,620 --> 00:34:00,500
the first cup.

583
00:34:01,520 --> 00:34:02,530
I've got to keep

584
00:34:03,350 --> 00:34:05,850
my pride intact, haven't I?

585
00:34:09,880 --> 00:34:10,300
Your wish is granted.

586
00:34:10,520 --> 00:34:11,420
Thank you, Your Highness.

587
00:34:11,670 --> 00:34:13,900
I'll go get the liquor now.

588
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:17,020
Wait.

589
00:34:22,630 --> 00:34:27,780
Someone just whispered something in my ear.

590
00:34:29,590 --> 00:34:33,030
I saw Shen Yong leave your side not long ago.

591
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:35,650
Could it be that Mr. Shen said something to you?

592
00:34:36,550 --> 00:34:39,050
No. It was a woman.

593
00:34:41,150 --> 00:34:42,050
A woman?

594
00:34:42,800 --> 00:34:44,340
What was she saying?

595
00:34:46,320 --> 00:34:47,250
Your Highness.

596
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:48,690
- You've had too much to drink. - Go away!

597
00:34:48,700 --> 00:34:50,840
Your Highness, I'm coming in.

598
00:34:51,320 --> 00:34:53,180
Your Highness sure know how to make an escape,

599
00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:55,160
sneaking off here to avoid drinking,

600
00:34:55,520 --> 00:34:56,940
and on top of that, you forgot all about me.

601
00:35:00,230 --> 00:35:03,340
I was wondering which courtesan was putting on such airs.

602
00:35:03,840 --> 00:35:05,250
Turns out it's you, Liuchu.

603
00:35:06,710 --> 00:35:08,740
Your Highness is hosting a banquet at the Zhen Tower today.

604
00:35:09,070 --> 00:35:10,720
How could I not come to join the fun?

605
00:35:11,710 --> 00:35:12,380
Your Highness,

606
00:35:12,630 --> 00:35:13,730
I asked you just now

607
00:35:14,040 --> 00:35:15,820
what outfit you liked on me,

608
00:35:16,070 --> 00:35:17,610
and which dance you wanted to see.

609
00:35:17,960 --> 00:35:18,690
But you

610
00:35:19,190 --> 00:35:20,420
didn't even say a word.

611
00:35:23,110 --> 00:35:23,820
Is that so?

612
00:35:25,630 --> 00:35:28,280
I came today without letting you know in advance.

613
00:35:28,920 --> 00:35:30,130
You're not upset with me, are you?

614
00:35:31,590 --> 00:35:33,500
You gave me such a pleasant surprise.

615
00:35:34,150 --> 00:35:35,820
How could I possibly be upset with you?

616
00:35:42,230 --> 00:35:43,020
Liuchu,

617
00:35:43,630 --> 00:35:44,900
come meet someone.

618
00:35:45,150 --> 00:35:48,050
This is a new friend of mine.

619
00:35:49,190 --> 00:35:51,120
So, he is...

620
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:54,690
I am the Imperial Astronomer,

621
00:35:55,270 --> 00:35:56,020
- Zang Hai. - Yes, that's right.

622
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:58,090
You are quite good-looking.

623
00:36:00,230 --> 00:36:02,730
Greetings, Miss Liuchu.

624
00:36:04,000 --> 00:36:04,650
Miss?

625
00:36:07,630 --> 00:36:09,780
It's been ages since anyone's called me that.

626
00:36:10,110 --> 00:36:11,570
How refreshing.

627
00:36:13,710 --> 00:36:14,500
Your Highness,

628
00:36:15,110 --> 00:36:17,380
I've prepared a special dance for the occasion.

629
00:36:17,750 --> 00:36:20,380
Would you care to come take a look?

630
00:36:21,070 --> 00:36:21,820
Sure,

631
00:36:22,360 --> 00:36:23,340
Miss Liuchu.

632
00:36:46,920 --> 00:36:47,860
Might Your Highness

633
00:36:48,000 --> 00:36:50,340
kindly tell me more about Mr. Kuai?

634
00:36:51,040 --> 00:36:53,500
Kuai Duo was a man of great talent,

635
00:36:54,190 --> 00:36:55,090
yet he died all the same.

636
00:36:55,520 --> 00:36:57,900
His whole family was burned beyond recognition,

637
00:36:57,920 --> 00:36:59,090
and not a single soul survived.

638
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:02,050
You seem quite interested in Kuai Duo's death.

639
00:37:02,750 --> 00:37:05,730
The treasure you're talking about is the Gui Seal, isn't it?

640
00:37:06,150 --> 00:37:10,300
My father died because of the Gui Seal.

641
00:37:11,070 --> 00:37:11,860
Even I

642
00:37:12,230 --> 00:37:14,130
have never seen the Gui Seal myself.

643
00:37:14,440 --> 00:37:15,980
I, too, am very curious about it.

644
00:38:08,670 --> 00:38:09,340
You are awake.

645
00:38:12,550 --> 00:38:13,380
Master Liuchu.

646
00:38:16,150 --> 00:38:17,380
You drank so much.

647
00:38:17,960 --> 00:38:20,570
You probably don't even remember how you got into the carriage.

648
00:38:23,550 --> 00:38:24,940
It's a shame that after all that talking,

649
00:38:25,750 --> 00:38:29,420
I still can't be sure if Prince Yongrong is the third person.

650
00:38:34,070 --> 00:38:34,690
It's not him.

651
00:38:35,270 --> 00:38:36,250
You don't need to investigate anymore.

652
00:38:39,070 --> 00:38:40,860
When misfortune befell your family,

653
00:38:41,190 --> 00:38:42,860
His Highness was attending a night banquet.

654
00:38:43,440 --> 00:38:45,690
Was it the very night my family was wiped out?

655
00:38:48,750 --> 00:38:49,980
So many years have passed,

656
00:38:50,880 --> 00:38:53,860
yet I still remember the fire that night.

657
00:38:55,840 --> 00:38:58,530
The banquet was held on a luxurious boat,

658
00:38:59,110 --> 00:39:00,180
and I was there as well.

659
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:02,530
At dusk, everyone boarded the boat,

660
00:39:03,510 --> 00:39:06,100
which sailed northeast

661
00:39:06,520 --> 00:39:08,300
along the Guangji River.

662
00:39:09,040 --> 00:39:10,050
We only docked at dawn,

663
00:39:10,880 --> 00:39:12,450
and it was His Highness who first noticed

664
00:39:13,360 --> 00:39:15,640
the distant sky glowing red.

665
00:39:16,710 --> 00:39:18,020
Only then did everyone step outside to take a look.

666
00:39:22,380 --> 00:39:23,340
That means

667
00:39:24,360 --> 00:39:25,650
none of the guests at the banquet that night

668
00:39:27,230 --> 00:39:29,130
could have been involved in the massacre of my family.

669
00:39:29,800 --> 00:39:30,420
Yes.

670
00:39:31,040 --> 00:39:33,510
As soon as Gao Ming told me you were going to visit His Highness,

671
00:39:33,590 --> 00:39:35,170
I rushed over

672
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:37,250
so you wouldn't waste your effort.

673
00:39:41,190 --> 00:39:43,340
Thank you, Master, for coming to help me today.

674
00:40:05,320 --> 00:40:06,560
This helps with hangovers.

675
00:40:06,710 --> 00:40:08,910
Dissolve it and have him drink it.

676
00:40:09,670 --> 00:40:10,130
All right.

677
00:40:12,190 --> 00:40:13,520
Good thing you informed me,

678
00:40:13,750 --> 00:40:16,420
otherwise he might not have made it through today.

679
00:40:17,630 --> 00:40:19,050
He set out before completing his training,

680
00:40:19,270 --> 00:40:20,940
so he's not exactly fully prepared.

681
00:40:21,670 --> 00:40:22,250
Right.

682
00:40:22,710 --> 00:40:25,460
So, if he were like you, he'd manage just fine?

683
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:28,570
Of course. I'm his master, after all.

684
00:40:30,190 --> 00:40:30,690
I'm leaving.

685
00:40:32,190 --> 00:40:32,860
You're leaving already?

686
00:40:56,040 --> 00:40:56,570
Hai?

687
00:40:57,880 --> 00:40:59,050
Master, please come in.

688
00:41:02,710 --> 00:41:03,530
You're up.

689
00:41:05,230 --> 00:41:06,250
I made you some congee.

690
00:41:06,590 --> 00:41:07,090
Come.

691
00:41:08,070 --> 00:41:09,050
Thank you, Master.

692
00:41:12,110 --> 00:41:12,530
Here.

693
00:41:13,400 --> 00:41:13,860
Have some.

694
00:41:15,960 --> 00:41:16,500
How do you feel?

695
00:41:17,000 --> 00:41:17,730
Are you sober now?

696
00:41:18,920 --> 00:41:20,650
You came back last night and said nothing.

697
00:41:20,920 --> 00:41:22,300
I was worried you'd wake up

698
00:41:22,300 --> 00:41:23,300
and forget everything.

699
00:41:25,400 --> 00:41:26,380
Did you find any leads?

700
00:41:29,320 --> 00:41:30,450
Throughout last night,

701
00:41:30,750 --> 00:41:32,340
I was suspicious of Prince Yongrong,

702
00:41:33,520 --> 00:41:34,860
but Master Liuchu's words

703
00:41:35,750 --> 00:41:37,340
made me completely dismiss those doubts.

704
00:41:45,480 --> 00:41:46,050
That said,

705
00:41:47,040 --> 00:41:49,860
a person brought up during the night banquet

706
00:41:50,800 --> 00:41:51,860
caught my attention.

707
00:41:53,550 --> 00:41:54,050
Who is it?

708
00:41:55,190 --> 00:41:57,500
Mr. Zhao Bingwen, Minister of Revenue.

709
00:42:01,040 --> 00:42:02,020
Is there a problem with Mr. Zhao?

710
00:42:04,230 --> 00:42:06,730
He's not directly related to my family's massacre,

711
00:42:07,880 --> 00:42:08,940
but after the incident,

712
00:42:09,480 --> 00:42:11,340
he did petition His Majesty to punish the culprits harshly,

713
00:42:12,440 --> 00:42:15,260
resulting in the execution of all those bandits.

714
00:42:15,750 --> 00:42:16,530
Those bandits

715
00:42:17,110 --> 00:42:19,340
were either bought off or tortured into confessing.

716
00:42:19,920 --> 00:42:20,860
Either way,

717
00:42:21,710 --> 00:42:23,430
if even one of them lives,

718
00:42:23,670 --> 00:42:25,210
the truth will inevitably be exposed.

719
00:42:25,960 --> 00:42:27,170
However, what Mr. Zhao did

720
00:42:27,880 --> 00:42:28,860
is understandable.

721
00:42:31,190 --> 00:42:32,340
My father was an upright man,

722
00:42:32,880 --> 00:42:34,610
and it's natural that some officials in the court

723
00:42:35,150 --> 00:42:36,090
were filled with righteous indignation.

724
00:42:37,550 --> 00:42:38,050
But

725
00:42:39,070 --> 00:42:40,170
as long as there's even a slight chance

726
00:42:40,200 --> 00:42:41,570
that a third party is covering up the truth,

727
00:42:42,670 --> 00:42:43,570
I won't let it go.

728
00:42:47,590 --> 00:42:48,300
Yes.

729
00:42:49,520 --> 00:42:50,730
After all, this is the only lead

730
00:42:50,750 --> 00:42:52,250
we have now.

731
00:42:53,230 --> 00:42:56,900
It seems I must find a way to meet him.

732
00:43:22,300 --> 00:43:26,980
♪Conceal the ambition in my eyes♪

733
00:43:29,460 --> 00:43:36,140
♪In my palm, I hold a dangerous desire♪

734
00:43:36,660 --> 00:43:39,420
♪Turbulent waves hidden in my sleeves♪

735
00:43:40,020 --> 00:43:42,740
♪Silent thunder echoes around♪

736
00:43:43,020 --> 00:43:44,980
♪However cunning you are♪

737
00:43:45,460 --> 00:43:47,540
♪I can see♪

738
00:43:49,260 --> 00:43:51,380
♪Right through you♪

739
00:43:57,740 --> 00:44:04,780
♪Schemes are my armor♪

740
00:44:04,940 --> 00:44:10,380
♪Overt plans are my weapons♪

741
00:44:11,940 --> 00:44:14,660
♪With restrained fury♪

742
00:44:15,340 --> 00:44:18,020
♪I purge the world's corruption♪

743
00:44:18,220 --> 00:44:20,260
♪The night is not dark♪

744
00:44:20,740 --> 00:44:22,820
♪Because♪

745
00:44:23,940 --> 00:44:29,420
♪My heart burns bright♪

746
00:44:32,220 --> 00:44:35,500
♪I control the shifting clouds♪

747
00:44:35,700 --> 00:44:38,260
♪I command the falling rain♪

748
00:44:38,420 --> 00:44:40,780
♪The compass of the human soul is unpredictable♪

749
00:44:40,900 --> 00:44:45,700
♪There will always be ups and downs♪

750
00:44:46,180 --> 00:44:49,500
♪I hold the power of life and death♪

751
00:44:49,700 --> 00:44:52,260
♪I grant and I take away♪

752
00:44:52,420 --> 00:44:55,940
♪When faith burns like the scorching sun♪

753
00:44:55,980 --> 00:44:59,460
♪I will sing aloud with you♪

754
00:44:59,580 --> 00:45:02,820
♪I am the sowing season♪

755
00:45:02,940 --> 00:45:06,220
♪I am the autumn harvest♪

756
00:45:06,460 --> 00:45:08,620
♪I am the world♪

757
00:45:08,820 --> 00:45:12,380
♪I am the people♪

758
00:45:13,580 --> 00:45:16,660
♪And you are also me♪
